真係好鍾意用錢堆砌感情嘅，就好應該發憤<br />\n老實講，買部iPhone都用你一半糧.......都係有啲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8ee8d2f0366fd56f535dbba1078628a9e9fa75e8","tid":45243,"uid":46534,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-19T01:02:34.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>生日快樂<br />\n算吧啦，又俾帽你載又喺正生日前同你講分手<br />\n佢仲洗你咁多錢，𡃶你想同你過世嘅話點捨得你為佢洗哂分糧？<br />\n早走早著<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n巴打慢慢嚟<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/05.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n佢成日嗌我唔好,係我堅持話要<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n一個好對象嘅條件之一係成熟，唔會亂洗錢，對將來有打算<br />\n你咁樣洗錢法，你個ex唔俾帽你戴，遲早都會嫌棄你<br />\n要氹人可以整手工（如果對方鍾意），可以煮下野食<br />\n你買個教訓，新嘅一歲好好學下啲技能氹女女<br />\n你真係好鍾意用錢堆砌感情嘅，就好應該發憤<br />\n老實講，<span style=\"color: red;\">買部iPhone都用你一半糧</span>.......都係有啲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n自膠睇錯<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n但係都係果個意思，出一半錢買iPhone都話chur，真係唔掂<br />\n巴打發憤賺多啲啦"},{"pid":"848a6990745b9a0b72d411e333c1a72ae2d6f4b4","tid":45243,"uid":27447,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-19T01:03:07.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/green_cap_3.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c706c3b29debca406b98e4ddb5c247762f6a993d","tid":45243,"uid":59425,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-19T01:05:18.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>因咩事分手<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote